J.W.B., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF REVENUE CHILD SUPPORT, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-5085 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 7, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The motion to dismiss appeal as moot filed by appellee, Department of Revenue, is granted, and this appeal is dismissed as moot. Appellant's response to the motion to dismiss is noted.

LaROSE, C.J., and SILBERMAN and VILLANTI, JJ., Concur.
